### 0. Registrar Usuario
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Franco",
  "apellido": "Barrabino",
  "email": "abc@hot.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### 1. Loguearse para obtener el Token
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "abc@hot.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

